------------------
INSTALATION
------------------
To install GX Dusky Sky simply uncompress the zip inside the ".themes" folder in your home directory and then choose it with your favourite app.

Notice that ".themes" is a hidden folder, you should press Ctrl+H to make it visible. If you the directory does not exist, you can create manually.

